<item>
            <title>[FELIX-279] Concurrency Issues when enabling components</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-279</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When bundles are started and their components registered, enabled and activated and configuration is provided to them, timing issues may occurr, such that in the end some components may not be started at all.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12368541">FELIX-279</key>
            <summary>Concurrency Issues when enabling components</summary>
